#: ../../T/the-literature.rst:5
msgid "the literature"
msgstr "the literature"

#: ../../T/the-literature.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../T/the-literature.rst:9
msgid ""
"Computer-science journals and other publications, vaguely gestured at to "
"answer a question that the speaker believes is :ref:`trivial`\\. Thus, one "
"might answer an annoying question by saying \"It's in the literature.\" "
"Oppose :ref:`Knuth`\\, which has no connotation of triviality."
msgstr ""
"コンピュータ科学の雑誌やその他の出版物。話し手が\\ :ref:`trivial`\\ "
"だと考える質問に答えるために、漠然と指し示される。こうして、うっとうしい質問には「それは文献に載っている」と答えることになる。\\ "
":ref:`Knuth`\\ と対比せよ。こちらは些末さの含みを持たない。"
